{
  "stem": "22660.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only after it blew up in our faces, then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Really not so much before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am sure my parents with each other, and my parents with my grandparents. we were really not burdened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, little by little, customers would take the business away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But very little by little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- I think maybe up to '36 or '37, his business was still OK.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it just started, I would say, in '38 that really-- now we didn't have any help in the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now they're called us Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And now, business did get lack-- you know, get-- got much more lax.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1938, it was very, very noticeable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew then that something had to be done.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was always that we would like to come to the United States, and that was just not possible for us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at the very end, my grandmother knew the secretary of the Uruguayan consul in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was very wealthy, so with giving her money and doing what she could, she ultimately got a tourist visa for my parents and us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, the big problem was a tourist visa-- just what it says.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can go for a year out to that country, but you have to come back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then that was the most horrendous story that I have to tell up to that point.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the only way that you would really receive that tourist visa was if the head of the Gestapo in Hamburg gave you permission to return to Germany, to return to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, you know that that was-- obviously, nobody would do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, my brother and I were outside-- that was during the time that my father was in the Catholic hospital.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
